>WebGLContextEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/WebGLFramebuffer\"><code>WebGLFramebuffer</code></a></li><li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"Cette documentation n'a pas encore été rédigée, vous pouvez aider en contribuant&nbsp;!\"><code>WebGLObject</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/WebGLProgram\"><code>WebGLProgram</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLQuery\"><code>WebGLQuery</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLRenderbuffer\"><code>WebGLRenderbuffer</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLSampler\"><code>WebGLSampler</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/WebGLShader\"><code>WebGLShader</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLShaderPrecisionFormat\"><code>WebGLShaderPrecisionFormat</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLSync\"><code>WebGLSync</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/WebGLTexture\"><code>WebGLTexture</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLTransformFeedback\"><code>WebGLTransformFeedback</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLUniformLocation\"><code>WebGLUniformLocation</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLVertexArrayObject\"><code>WebGLVertexArrayObject</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>Les méthodes <strong><code>WebGLRenderingContext.uniformMatrix[234]fv()</code></strong> de l'<a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/WebGL_API\">API WebGL</a> définissent des valeurs matricielles pour les variables uniform.</p>\n<p>Les trois versions de cette méthode (<code>uniformMatrix2fv()</code>, <code>uniformMatrix3fv()</code> et <code>unifomMatrix4fv()</code>) prennent comme valeur d'entrée des vecteurs à 2, 3 et 4 composantes, respectivement.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntaxe","title":"Syntaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>WebGLRenderingContext<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">uniformMatrix2fv</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>emplacement<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> transposer<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> valeur<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nWebGLRenderingContext<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">uniformMatrix3fv</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>emplacement<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> transposer<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> valeur<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nWebGLRenderingContext<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">uniformMatrix4fv</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>emplacement<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> transposer<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> valeur<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"paramètres","title":"Paramètres","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"emplacement\"><code>emplacement</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Un objet <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLUniformLocation\"><code>WebGLUniformLocation</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> contenant l'emplacement de l'attribut uniform à modifier. L'emplacement est obtenu en utilisant <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/WebGLRenderingContext/getAttribLocation\" title=\"getAttribLocation()\"><code>getAttribLocation()</code></a>.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"transposer\"><code>transposer</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Un <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGL_API/Types\"><code>GLboolean</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> indiquant si la matrice doit être transposée. Doit être <code>false</code>.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"valeur\"><code>valeur</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Un <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Float32Array\"><code>Float32Array</code></a> ou une suite de valeurs <code>GLfloat</code>.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"valeur_retournée","title":"Valeur retournée","isH3":true,"content":"<p><code>undefined</code></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemples","title":"Exemples","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>gl<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">uniformMatrix2fv</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>loc<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">2.1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2.2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Spécifications","id":"spécifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://www.khronos.org/registry/webgl/specs/latest/1.0/#5.14.10","title":"WebGL Specification"}],"query":"api.WebGLRenderingContext.uniformMatrix2fv"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilité des navigateurs","id":"compatibilité_des_navigateurs","isH3":false,"query":"api.WebGLRenderingContext.uniformMatrix2fv","dataURL":"/fr/docs/Web/API/WebGLRenderingContext/uniformMatrix/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"voir_aussi","title":"Voir aussi","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/WebGLRenderingContext/uniform\"><code>WebGLRenderingContext.uniform()</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGL2RenderingContext/uniformMatrix\"><code>WebGL2RenderingContext.uniformMatrix()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> – versions WebGL 2 de ces méthodes.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntaxe","id":"syntaxe"},{"text":"Exemples","id":"exemples"},{"text":"Spécifications","id":"spécifications"},{"text":"Compatibilité des navigateurs","id":"compatibilité_des_navigateurs"},{"text":"Voir aussi","id":"voir_aussi"}],"summary":"Les méthodes WebGLRenderingContext.uniformMatrix[234]fv() de l'API WebGL définissent des valeurs matricielles pour les variables uniform.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"WebGLRenderingContext.uniformMatrix[234]fv()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"WebGLRenderingContext.uniformMatrix[234]fv()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"WebGLRenderingContext.uniformMatrix[234]fv()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"fr/web/api/webglrenderingcontext/uniformmatrix","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/fr/web/api/webglrenderingcontext/uniformmatrix/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921